title: Military Construction and Veterans Affairs, Agriculture, and Legislative Branch Appropriations Act, 2026

other_titles.title: Military Construction, Veterans Affairs, and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2026
Making appropriations for military construction, the Department of Veterans Affairs, and related agencies for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2026, and for other purposes.
